T1  - NEW EXPORTER DYNAMICS
AU  - Ruhl, Kim J.
AU  - Willis, Jonathan L.
Y1  - 2017/08/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12232
T2  - International Economic Review
