T1  - EMPLOYMENT ADJUSTMENT AND LABOR UTILIZATION
AU  - Trapeznikova, Ija
Y1  - 2017/08/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12239
T2  - International Economic Review
